b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2668,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Gala Dragalia Remix Is Coming Soon!","message":"<div>Gala Dragalia Remix starts on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1639548000\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?<\/div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5\\u2605 adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5\\u2605 summon or 5\\u2605 featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">The newly added 5\\u2605 adventurer Ayaha &amp; Otoha (flame\/staff) will also appear in subsequent summon showcases.<\/span><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\"><br><\/span><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">Adventurers and dragons added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase as well. For information about which adventurers and dragons may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.<\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcNewly added featured adventurer:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Ayaha &amp; Otoha (flame\/staff)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcFeatured adventurer from past Gala Dragalia summon showcases:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Gala Leonidas (flame\/rapid-fire manacaster)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcFeatured dragon from past Gala Dragalia summon showcases:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Gala Reborn Agni (flame)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">The following limited-time adventurers and dragon will make their return in this Gala Dragalia Remix but are not featured.<\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Adventurers<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Dragonyule Lily (water\/staff)<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Dragonyule Victor (shadow\/axe)<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Dragonyule Malora (light\/axe)<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Dragonyule Cleo (water\/dagger)<\/div><div>4\\u2605 Dragonyule Nefaria (water\/bow)<\/div><div>4\\u2605 Dragonyule Xander (water\/wand)<\/div><div>4\\u2605 Dragonyule Xainfried (wind\/wand)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Dragon<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Dragonyule Jeanne (water)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix event duration:<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1639548000\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1639979999\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurers and dragon below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Featured adventurers:<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/bbabe4198ff0cc8846e32165538ea51e.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>80<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/5d54775020f2b8c24e8e1d445b58d2ad2.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>765<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>492<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>2,497<\/span>\\n                <\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Adventurer Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>Twin sisters who were once part of Agito. Ayaha<br>has black hair, Otoha white\\u2014and though both are<br>innocent and cruel, they believe their brand of<br>freedom is the only correct one. They have been<br>acting of their own accord since Agito\'s end.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/d07d9921bf8130db4dfafb43dde61cc52.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Nabe Nabe Sokonuke<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to the target and nearby enemies,<br>partially fills the dragon gauge if the attack<br>connects, removes all afflictions from the entire<br>team, and swaps the user from Ayaha to Otoha<br>or vice versa. If this skill is used directly after<br>Onigokko or Kagome Kagome, it will also<br>immediately ready Onigokko and Kagome Kagome<br>for use.<br><br>If this skill is used while shapeshifted, a variant<br>called Hana Ichi Monme will be used instead.<br>Hana Ichi Monme deals damage to the target<br>and nearby enemies, draws them together,<br>inflicts stun, burn, and scorchrend, and restores<br>HP relative to the amount of damage dealt.<br>Hana Ichi Monme also grants the entire team<br>a team strength amp, the \\"Purple Hagoromo\\"<br>effect, and increases their max HP.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 81 \\u00d7 14 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 8,364<br>Dragon Energy Gained: 40<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbAffliction Recovery (All Afflictions)<br><br><color=#00008B>When Shapeshifted:<\/color><br>Damage: 396 \\u00d7 7 hits<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbHP +15%<br>\\u30fbPurple Hagoromo<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u3000\\u3000HP Regen<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 2% of max HP<br>\\u3000\\u3000Stunned Punisher +10%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Burning Punisher +5%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Scorchrent Punisher +5%<br>\\u30fbStun<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 7 seconds<br>\\u30fbBurn<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 12 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 3.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 97<br>\\u30fbScorchrend<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 21 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 41<br>Team Amps:<br>\\u30fbTeam Strength Amp (MAX Lv. = 1)<br>\\u30fbHP Drain<br>\\u3000\\u3000Recovers 10% of damage dealt<br>\\u3000\\u3000Recovers up to 10% of targeted unit\'s max HP<br>\\u3000\\u3000Target: Entire Team<br><\/div><\/dd><dt class=\\"skill-cost-wrap\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/3171d52c1cdee5d533d25df908ef96252.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Onigokko & Kagome Kagome<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"skill-cost\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shareable<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"txt-num\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>6<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>If this skill is used as Ayaha, the Onigokko<br>variant will be used. Onigokko deals damage<br>to the target and nearby enemies, inflicts stun,<br>restores HP to all teammates, and grants them<br>the \\"Blue Hagoromo\\" effect.<br><br>If this skill is used as Otoha, the Kagome Kagome<br>variant will be used. Kagome Kagome deals<br>damage to multiple targets and enemies near<br>those targets, inflicts burn and scorchrend,<br>restores HP to all teammates, and grants them<br>overdamage and the \\"Red Hagoromo\\" effect.<br>This skill\'s attack will only affect each target<br>once per use.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\"><color=#00008B>As Ayaha:<\/color><br>Damage: 1,395 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Recovery Potency: 60<br>Skill Energy Required: 4,132<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 16,395<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbStun<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 6 seconds<br>\\u30fbBlue Hagoromo<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Stacks up to 3 times<br>\\u3000\\u3000Wind Res +4<br>\\u3000\\u3000HP Regen<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 18<br><br><color=#00008B>As Otoha:<\/color><br>Damage: 1,048 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Recovery Potency: 60<br>Skill Energy Required: 4,132<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbRed Hagoromo<br>\\u3000\\u3000Affliction Success Rate +50%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Stacks up to 3 times<br>\\u30fbOverdamage<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 40% of strength<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbBurn<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 12 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 3.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 72.7<br>\\u30fbScorchrend<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 21 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 31<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Dragon Damage +20%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tAdds 20% to the modifier applied to damage<br>when in dragon form. Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/5a96ba5664709010ecaad36c8d6332792.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Flame) Combo = Buff Skill Time +15%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Flame: <br>increases duration of their buff skills by 15%<br>when the combo count is 10 or higher.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/c0668faa3dc59d6a25d13c11b55642532.png\\"><\/span><span>Union II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>The user begins quests as Ayaha but can swap<br>to Otoha and vice versa by using Nabe Nabe<br>Sokonuke. Ayaha and Otoha share all the same<br>stats, but their standard attacks, force strike,<br>dash attack, and second skill differ.<br><br>Force strike effects:<br>Ayaha: Deals damage to enemies in a line and<br>reduces their strength by 5% for 20 seconds.<br>This strength reduction will not stack.<br>Otoha: Deals damage to surrounding enemies.<br><br>When shapeshifting, the user will transform<br>into Beast Ayaha & Otoha regardless of what<br>dragon they are equipped with and activate the<br>following effects while shapeshifted:<br>\\u30fbThe user\'s shapeshift time is extended by 25%.<br>\\u30fbThe user\'s standard attacks lower enemy burn<br>or scorchrend resistance by 20% for 30 seconds.<br>Both of these resistance reduction effects can be<br>applied simultaneously, but neither of them will<br>stack.<br>\\u30fbThe user is granted a dragon strike that deals<br>damage to surrounding enemies and inflicts stun<br>and scorchrend.<br><br>In addition, the user\'s dragon skill level will<br>match the level of the adventurer\'s initial skill,<br>displayed at the top of their skill list.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/6a94f7adaeafadf56700005abbf6d8fe2.png\\"><\/span><span>Warabe Asobi II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Using Nabe Nabe Sokonuke reduces<br>susceptibility to afflictions by 20% for<br>the remainder of the quest.<br>This reduction can stack up to five times.<br><br>Also, using Nabe Nabe Sokonuke, Onigokko,<br>or Kagome Kagome will grant the user a<br>strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of one. After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for eight seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/cb8b9d60b801a6b11eda8d8e40214f1f2.png\\"><\/span><span>Tosenbo & Toryanse II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces damage taken by 10% when not<br>inflicted with any afflictions.<br><br>Also, grants the user a stack of the \\"Playtime\\"<br>effect for every nine seconds that pass in which<br>the user is not inflicted with any afflictions.<br>During Playtime, the user\'s strength is increased<br>by 5% and the potency of recovery skills by 10%.<br>This buff can stack up to three times. All stacks<br>will be lost upon being inflicted with an affliction.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Regarding Ayaha &amp; Otoha&#39;s Shared Skill<br>This adventurer&#39;s shared skill is the Onigokko variant that is used while Ayaha is active.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/aaeba653546955c357e4715bd20573ff.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>80<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/5d54775020f2b8c24e8e1d445b58d2ad2.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>754<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>505<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>2,499<\/span>\\n                <\/div><div class=\\"available-mode\\">\\n                        <div class=\\"txt\\"><span>Available Modes<\/span><\/div>\\n                        <div class=\\"icon\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/4805e47916f093eb2b9049cff29e9eb72.png\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/d45c68ecb3b1d88cba2136c949f214772.png\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1f0f10277cfc223cafe9e19e2d15434d2.png\\"><\/div><\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Adventurer Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>The first scion of the Kingdom of Alberia.<br>He seeks to unify not only South Grastaea, but<br>the whole of the world in order to free it from the<br>dragons\' rule. As proof of his resolve, he has<br>taken on brilliant crimson garb.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt class=\\"skill-cost-wrap\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/775392a8a09a554df496b2a54960c3e62.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Sovereign Barrage<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"skill-cost\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shareable<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"txt-num\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>5<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and inflicts scorchrend.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 100 \\u00d7 18 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 3,780<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 7,975<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbScorchrend<br>\\u3000Lasts 21 seconds<br>\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000Damage: 41.6<br><\/div><\/dd><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/d06b5882930f12e76cbac51669f220ff2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Absolute Dominion<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to surrounding enemies,<br>dispels one buff from each target, and grants<br>the user the \\"Draconian Grace\\" effect.<br><br>Draconian Grace has five progressively more <br>powerful levels.<br>Lv. 1: For 40 seconds, reduces damage taken by 10%.<br>Lv. 2: For 40 seconds, increases strength by 5%,<br>and reduces damage taken by 10%.<br>Lv. 3: For 40 seconds, increases strength by 5%,<br>and reduces damage taken by 15%.<br>Lv. 4: For 40 seconds, increases strength by 10%,<br>and reduces damage taken by 20%.<br>Lv. 5: For the remainder of the quest, increases<br>strength by 10%, and reduces damage taken by 20%.<br><br>If Draconian Grace is granted while already active,<br>it will be raised one level. Conversely, it will be<br>lowered one level when the effect\'s remaining time<br>is depleted. If the effect is at level one when this<br>time is depleted, it will instead be removed entirely.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 300 \\u00d7 7 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 7,560<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbDispels Buffs<br>\\u30fbDraconian Grace<br>\\u3000Lasts 40 seconds<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/85285afa2a77c2880c1c006d8d0d214c2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Gauge Accelerator +20%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tSpeeds the rate the mode gauge decreases<br>by 20%. Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/de137cf7302f5717d1be863dbd4a45e62.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Flame) Combo = Shapeshift Prep V<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Flame:<br>fills 3% of their dragon gauge<br>for every 50-hit combo.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/054d33d79920a0e51bbbb11909b08bf92.png\\"><\/span><span>Conquering Scion II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>When shapeshifting, Leonidas will transform<br>into Mars regardless of what dragon he is<br>equipped with.<br>When the \\"Draconian Grace Lv. 5\\" effect is active,<br>Leonidas\'s shapeshift time will be halved,<br>but the amount of the dragon gauge consumed<br>by shapeshifting will also be halved.<br>If Leonidas shapeshifts while this effect is active,<br>Draconian Grace Lv. 5 will be consumed when<br>his shapeshift is undone.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/ea4c47784ca6465117276eb2a3d9a0d92.png\\"><\/span><span>Conqueror\'s Will II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun and sleep by 100%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/62ec54c3111dcff5d7c6fadf0c9e0ae92.png\\"><\/span><span>Ruthless Ignition II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases damage to scorchrent enemies by 30%<br>and damage to enemies in overdrive state by 10%.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities and represent the adventurers at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div>\\u30fbAdventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.<\/div><div>\\u30fbSome skills have different effects when used as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Featured dragon:<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/2b260d2b6a1b1c3fff8281591de1e2be.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>369<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>127<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>1,296<\/span>\\n                <\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Dragon Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>The rapacious dragon Agni, once feared as the<br>Firelord, reborn. His heart resonated with the<br>people\'s hunger for peace, freeing him from the<br>miasma that once ate away at him. His hunger<br>only burns hotter now, fit to reduce all to ash.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/b3eeeb36b0d4aed9820f32abb1dd51022.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Blazing Strike<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and inflicts scorchrend. Enemies in break state<br>take reduced damage. If the user is targeting<br>an enemy and not using a skill when their<br>remaining shapeshift time runs out, this skill<br>will be used automatically, regardless of<br>whether or not the skill gauge is filled.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 1,078 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Damage: 1,470 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbScorchrend<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 21 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 41.6<br>Damage Modifier:<br>\\u30fb75% against enemies in break state<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span><span>(Flame) Strength +70%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Flame: <br>increases strength by 70%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1ba1d939f31aa624b013b900d03a48812.png\\"><\/span><span>(Flame) Fervor of the Firelord II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Flame:<br>adds 30% to the modifier applied to damage<br>against wind-attuned enemies and enemies<br>with no attunement for 45 seconds every time<br>the dragon gauge fills by 10%. This increase<br>will not stack, and, after activating, this ability<br>will not activate again for five seconds.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe stats shown here represent the dragon at level 100, maximum bond, and unbound to the fourth stage. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.<\/div><div>2. Alberian Battle Royale skins for the adventurers featured in this summon showcase will go on sale and will cost fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1639461600,"prev_article_id":"2664","next_article_id":"2653","image_path":"","update_time":1639359716}}}'